```csharp
// Example: "v1.1.6" vs "1.2.0"
1. Strip 'v' prefix: "1.1.6" vs "1.2.0"
2. Try Version.TryParse() for semantic versioning
3. Compare using Version objects (1.2.0 > 1.1.6) âœ“
4. Fallback to string comparison if parsing fails
